# Client-Side Login and Registration Page

This project provides a basic client-side login and registration interface using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It is intended for demonstration or learning purposes and does not include any backend or server-side authentication.

## Features

- Separate forms for user login and registration
- Simple and clean user interface
- Basic form validation using JavaScript
- Responsive design for desktop and mobile devices

## File Structure

- index.html  
  Contains the structure for both login and registration forms.

- style.css  
  Provides styling for the forms and layout.

- script.js  
  Handles form switching and basic validation logic.


